  "text": "What is Content Engineering?\n\nAI isn’t magic.\nIt’s a toolbox.\n\nContent Engineering is what happens when you combine that toolbox with the craft of content creation and the rigor of software engineering.\n\nYou get:\n• Systems that create and retrieve the right content at the right time.\n• Accuracy from Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).\n• Brand voice baked into automation.\n\nThis is how thought leaders scale their reach without scaling effort.\n\n⚡ Welcome to the future of content.\n\n#ContentEngineering #GenAI #RAG",
